{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Client.type","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/type","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Service_Worker_API\">Service Worker API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client\"><code>Client</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/frameType\"><code>frameType</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/id\"><code>id</code></a></li><li><em><code>type</code></em></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/url\"><code>url</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/postMessage\"><code>postMessage()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Service Workers API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Cache\"><code>Cache</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CacheStorage\"><code>CacheStorage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clients\"><code>Clients</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ExtendableEvent\"><code>ExtendableEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FetchEvent\"><code>FetchEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/InstallEvent\"><code>InstallEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/serviceWorker\"><code>Navigator.serviceWorker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/NotificationEvent\"><code>NotificationEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PeriodicSyncEvent\"><code>PeriodicSyncEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PeriodicSyncManager\"><code>PeriodicSyncManager</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorker\"><code>ServiceWorker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerContainer\"><code>ServiceWorkerContainer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>ServiceWorkerGlobalScope</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerRegistration\"><code>ServiceWorkerRegistration</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SyncEvent\"><code>SyncEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SyncManager\"><code>SyncManager</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowClient\"><code>WindowClient</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client\"><code>Client</code></a> インターフェイスの <strong><code>type</code></strong> 読み取り専用プロパティは、サービスワーカーが制御しているクライアントの種類を示します。</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>myClientType</em> = <em>client</em>.type;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>クライアントの種類を表す文字列。 値は次のいずれかです。</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>\"window\"</code></li>\n <li><code>\"worker\"</code></li>\n <li><code>\"sharedworker\"</code></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js line-numbers  language-js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// サービスワーカークライアント（ドキュメントなど）</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">sendMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">message</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Promise</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> reject</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// これは ServiceWorker.postMessage バージョンであることに注意してください</span>\n    navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>serviceWorker<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>controller<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">postMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>message<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>serviceWorker<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onMessage</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">resolve</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 制御するサービスワーカー</span>\nself<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"message\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// e.source はクライアントオブジェクトです</span>\n  e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>source<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">postMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"こんにちは！ あなたのメッセージは: \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// type 値も投稿してクライアントに戻しましょう</span>\n  e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>source<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">postMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>source<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>type<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/ServiceWorker/#client-type\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Service Workers<br><small lang=\"ja\">type の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Client.type","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/type/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"Client インターフェイスの type 読み取り専用プロパティは、サービスワーカーが制御しているクライアントの種類を示します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Client.type","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/client/type","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/client/type/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client","title":"Client"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/type","title":"Client.type"}],"pageTitle":"Client.type - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}